premise_source_doc_sentence: iZombie  (  stylized as iZOMBiE  )  is an American television series developed by Rob Thomas and Diane Ruggiero-Wright for The CW , and is a loose adaptation of the comic book series of the same name created by Chris Roberson and Michael Allred , and published by DC Comics under their Vertigo imprint .
